## Python
```Python
from sympy.ntheory.primetest import is_square
from sympy.core.power import isqrt
from sympy import igcd
def a(n):
    k = -1
    while True:
        k += n
        s = isqrt(k) + 1
        m = pow(s, 2, n)
        if is_square(m):
            return igcd(n, s - isqrt(m))
print([a(n) for n in range(1, 87)])
```
